{
  "stem": "449.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we Jewish students, we had to-- to fight them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, they started to use the university for their Nazi propaganda, the swastikas, on the-- on the-- in the lecture hall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had-- we had to do something against it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we had quite the trouble with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And back to Egypt, when I was with Holzmann, I was very happy to have a nice position.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there came an influx from Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They came, young engineers, young work-- working men, all already with the Nazi spirit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they made my life miserable there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so I quit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- the-- in the work, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were we were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the desert surveying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to survey.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I needed their assistance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to cooperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- with purpose, they mixed up so that I shall come out with-- with results which did not-- did not fit the reality.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So surveying is a very delicate thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, if the-- the workers and the helpers want to to-- boycott, to obstruct, they can do it very easy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gave up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to Port Said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there I found also a nice job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The funny thing is that two of the-- of the people who were working with me in Suez in Holzmann, they came-- they were people who were holding the-- how do you-- you know what the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there is a stick to make the measurements.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The surveying equipment.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surveying, survey equipment--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
